19:07.261 --> 19:10.221
<b>...Dad's face again, right?</b>

19:17.811 --> 19:19.941
<b>Pink Hornet!</b>

19:23.361 --> 19:25.721
<b>That's Straw Hat! Shoot!</b>

19:30.241 --> 19:33.531
<b>You're really a high-maintenance brother.</b>

19:33.531 --> 19:34.651
<b>Reiju!</b>

19:45.631 --> 19:48.341
<b>Don't ever let him go!</b>

19:50.341 --> 19:51.091
<b>Step back!</b>

19:55.101 --> 19:58.851
<b>You have only one chance!
Don't ruin it!</b>

19:59.521 --> 20:03.111
<b>Sanji! You're a boy! Stop crying already!</b>

20:04.521 --> 20:08.111
<b>Listen! Don't ever come back here!</b>

20:08.111 --> 20:09.031
<b>Uh-huh!</b>

20:11.781 --> 20:14.411
<b>The sea is broad! You'll...</b>

20:16.491 --> 20:21.791
<b>You'll definitely meet kind people someday!!</b>

20:29.671 --> 20:32.771
<b><i>There's no way that you're a failure.</i></b>

20:33.801 --> 20:37.581
<b>Our mother protected her child 
at the risk of her own life and</b>

20:37.581 --> 20:39.851
<b>he was born with the spark of humanity.</b>

20:40.391 --> 20:42.961
<b>That child is you, Sanji.</b>

21:04.751 --> 21:07.381
<b>Run!!</b>

21:07.751 --> 21:09.301
<b>Don't look back!!</b>

21:13.681 --> 21:18.221
<b><i>Sanji... My little brother
who is the kindest person in the world!</i></b>

21:18.891 --> 21:19.851
<b>Reiju!</b>

21:21.311 --> 21:22.481
<b>Goodbye!</b>

22:01.471 --> 22:06.321
<b><i>Straw Hat and Sanji got off of the island!
Fleet, come in!</i></b>

22:08.191 --> 22:11.281
<b>Hurry up, Sanji!</b>

22:11.731 --> 22:13.321
<b>Sanji-<i>kun</i>...</b>

22:19.701 --> 22:20.991
<b>It's Sanji!</b>

22:21.541 --> 22:23.451
<b>Here he comes, guys!</b>

22:24.411 --> 22:26.961
<b>Sanji is carrying Luffy!</b>

22:28.961 --> 22:30.631
<b>Yay!</b>

22:30.631 --> 22:32.841
<b>I knew he could do it!</b>

22:32.841 --> 22:33.921
<b>Luffy!</b>

22:45.851 --> 22:48.811
<b>There it is, Luffy! The Sunny!</b>

22:49.271 --> 22:52.341
<b>Isn't dinner ready yet, Sanji?</b>

23:04.991 --> 23:08.231
<b><i>How will Bege's last big gamble end up?!</i></b>

23:08.231 --> 23:11.101
<b><i><i>All eyes throughout the country 
are on Mom and the cake!</i></i></b>

23:11.101 --> 23:14.071
<b><i>Meanwhile, the Sunny is in a 
joyous mood having Luffy back!</i></b>

23:14.071 --> 23:20.881
<b><i>However, Smoothie's cunning strategy puts them
in the greatest no-way-out danger ever!</i></b>

23:20.881 --> 23:25.301
<b>On the next episode of One Piece!
"The Last Hope! The Sun Pirates Emerge!"</b>

23:25.301 --> 23:28.051
<b>I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!</b>
